When we first met,
we sincerely liked each other.

277
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,970
 Which one do you like? Tell me. 

278
00:16:49,970 --> 00:16:51,420
 Cui, do you like this one? 

279
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:53,360
 Jeez. 

280
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:55,850
 The good ones are inside. 

281
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:18,940
