on Yan Huan's back?

303
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:50,020
I do.

304
00:18:50,020 --> 00:18:54,460
Has he ever told you about that?

305
00:18:57,620 --> 00:19:00,020
Never.

306
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,240
All right.

307
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:06,320
- Don't cry.
- That birthmark is truly a hard secret to dig.

308
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:12,320
There...

309
00:19:22,020 --> 00:19:25,180
Your face tells me things didn't go well.

310
00:19:25,180 --> 00:19:27,780
I spoke with Ms. Qing Er.

311
