354
00:22:28,660 --> 00:22:31,960
She's slender and beautiful.

355
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:33,120
Ru Ling must be here for me.

356
00:22:33,120 --> 00:22:35,060
No, I haven't seen her.

357
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:37,540
Thank you.

358
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:41,700
Ru Ling.

359
00:22:42,210 --> 00:22:43,320
Ru Ling.

360
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:46,360
Where did this little spirit come from? Don't get in my way.

361
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:50,520
Wait for me, Ru Ling!

362
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:24,820
 Nian Jiu was clearly last found here. 

363
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:30,340
Could it be... Could it be that Ting Yan's already...

