00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,660
You little spirit.

365
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:37,780
Why is it you again?

366
00:23:37,780 --> 00:23:40,096
 

367
00:23:41,540 --> 00:23:43,400
What does that mean?

368
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:45,400
I'm Ting Yan.

369
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:47,560
 Ting Yan? 

370
00:23:50,500 --> 00:23:52,380
It can't be.

371
00:23:57,600 --> 00:24:03,660
On Stargazing Terrace, Ting Yan gave me fruits, and we enjoyed the view.

372
00:24:03,660 --> 00:24:06,700
You really are Ting Yan?

373
00:24:06,700 --> 00:24:08,520
Ting Yan!

374
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:11,120
Oh, finally, my friend.

375
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:12,680
I understand now.

376
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:15,720
Grandmaster is trying to protect you this way

377
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:18,610
so you can avoid trouble
from the Eight Palaces.

378
00:24:19,360 --> 00:24:23,200
But it truly frightened me when I saw your life lamp go out.

379
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:26,980
It's always good to have friends.

380
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,940
Ru Ling.

381
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:34,880
Ru Ling, it's really you.

382
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,040
What brings you here?

383
00:24:36,040 --> 00:24:40,960
I came seeking Ting Yan,
so I happened to stop by here and found her.

384
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,960
You found Ting Yan?

385
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,560
Where's she?

386
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:54,380
- You don't know yet? 
 - No.

387
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:57,860
Don't worry. She's safe now.

388
00:24:57,860 --> 00:24:59,040
That's a relief.

389
00:24:59,040 --> 00:25:01,620
Looks like you two are tight.

390
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,900
Grandmaster.

391
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:12,680
I told Liao Ting Yan
to keep this secret from everyone.

392
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:15,520
She trusts you so much.

393
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:17,060
Forgive me, Grandmaster.

394
00:25:17,060 --> 00:25:21,480
I worry for Ting Yan and came looking for her.

395
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:25,080
Ting Yan couldn't bear to see me upset,
so she told me.

396
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:26,880
If you say a word about her whereabouts...

397
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,100
Please don't worry, Grandmaster.

398
00:25:28,100 --> 00:25:30,840
I will keep it to myself.

399
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:36,720
Grandmaster, Ru Ling,
you know where Ting Yan is,

400
00:25:36,720 --> 00:25:38,580
why won't you tell me?

401
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:41,520
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

402
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:44,300
Why don't you figure it out yourself?

403
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:51,780
Figure it out myself?

404
00:25:54,370 --> 00:25:57,920
Say, Ru Ling, now that we meet again,

405
00:25:57,920 --> 00:26:01,200
are you ready to begin the lessons?

406
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,520
Lessons?

407
00:26:02,520 --> 00:26:07,200
