463
00:29:20,080 --> 00:29:21,880
You're indeed a jerk.

464
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:23,160
You haven't even settled things
with Ms. Qing Er,

465
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,880
and now you're messing with Zhou Yue Qing.

466
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:26,880
I'm going to teach you a lesson.

