00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:38,160
Yue Qing.

471
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:40,760
Hold on.

472
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:44,800
 Our daughter was born last month. 

473
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:46,920
 This poor child doesn't have a name yet. 

474
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:50,360
 Will you give her a name? 

475
00:29:50,360 --> 00:29:54,480
 Huan once wrote me poems. 

476
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:57,220
 "We entrust our affection to the clear moon." 

477
00:29:57,220 --> 00:29:59,480
 "Let the breeze carry you away forever." 

478
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:03,440
Clear moon, breeze, Zhou.

479
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:06,180
My, my! This name is...

480
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:09,520
Yue Qing.
(T/N: Moon and breeze)

481
00:30:16,360 --> 00:30:18,840
Grandmaster, I think I've discovered
something important.

482
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:19,940
What's it?

483
00:30:19,940 --> 00:30:23,780
Yan Huan really likes Ms. Qing Er.

484
00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:31,260
You rushed here just to tell me Yan Huan's love story?

485
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:34,480
I just saw him
giving Ms. Qing Er's child a name.

486
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:38,320
Even if he truly likes her, so what?

487
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:40,280
Grandmaster, think about it.

488
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:43,000
For someone like Yan Huan,
who bluffs and flirts a lot,

489
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:46,800
if he really liked her, why wouldn't he marry Ms. Qing Er?

490
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:50,180
Why would he go to such lengths
to cut ties with her?

491
00:30:50,180 --> 00:30:52,920
Perhaps he has his own reasons,

492
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:55,780
and it might have something to do
with the flame-shaped birthmark.

493
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:01,560
Mr. Yan!

494
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:04,000
Mr. Yan, the 12th concubine
threw herself into the well!

495
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,920
What?

496
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:08,640
Luckily, she was saved.

497
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:10,120
Take me to her.

498
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:11,860
Mr. Yan, she's here.

499
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:13,940
My Xian!

500
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:17,860
Mr. Yan!

501
00:31:17,860 --> 00:31:21,240
Mr. Yan, please let me see my son.

502
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:24,320
Mr. Yan, if I weren't desperate to see my son,

503
00:31:24,320 --> 00:31:27,840
