505
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:30,560
Please.

506
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:32,640
Please let me see him.

507
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:36,800
Mr. Yan, I miss my child, too.

508
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:38,480
Mr. Yan.

509
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,360
Where's her son?

510
00:31:40,360 --> 00:31:41,760
I don't know, sir.

511
00:31:41,760 --> 00:31:45,840
The Master and you never allow us to ask about the children.

512
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:50,960
It seems like something's wrong
with this Master Yan.

513
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,500
Oh, right, Grandmaster.

514
00:31:52,500 --> 00:31:54,560
We've overlooked something.

515
00:31:54,560 --> 00:31:56,640
With so many concubines in the Yan Residence,

516
00:31:56,640 --> 00:32:00,160
there's no child here at all.

517
00:32:00,160 --> 00:32:03,640
I'm begging you, Mr. Yan.

518
00:32:03,640 --> 00:32:06,040
There's still one person who has a Yan child.

519
00:32:06,040 --> 00:32:08,040
Ms. Qing Er.

520
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:23,740
I saw Ms. Qing Er here last time.

521
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:26,520
She said she lives nearby.

522
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:32,560
Huan!

523
00:32:32,560 --> 00:32:36,200
- What's wrong, Ms. Qing Er?
- S-Someone took our child away.

524
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:37,840
- When did this happen?
- Just now.

525
00:32:37,840 --> 00:32:40,280
I was playing with the child in the courtyard.

526
00:32:40,280 --> 00:32:42,080
Then, I went inside to get her a pellet drum.

527
00:32:42,080 --> 00:32:44,920
