528
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:47,580
What should we do?

529
00:32:47,580 --> 00:32:48,840
I'll find her.

530
00:32:48,840 --> 00:32:50,400
But the streets are full of people.

531
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:52,120
